  "title": "PencilVoid's Distinctive Ores",
  "description": "More unique ore appearances",
  "body": "This pack gives ores unique and fun designs while remaining true to the vanilla style. The goal is to improve playability and accessibility by making each ore identifiable by shape. 1.17's texture update aimed to do something similar, but the shapes of the ores are largely random and hard to tell apart when colour is absent. This pack aims to rectify that.\n\nEach ore is given a stylised and thoughtful shape: gold forms shiny bars, lapis forms flowing waves, redstone forms circuit-like crystals. These all serve to give each ore its own identity and make them stand out.",
